 My Grandma]]''\n| Comedy\n| {{sort|2017-26-01|March 22, 2017}}\n| {{sort|109|1 season, 6 episodes}}\n| {{sort|022|22 min.}}\n| Ended\n|-\n| ''[[Good Game (2017 TV series)|Good Game]]''\n| Comedy\n| {{sort|2017-08-30|August 30, 2017}}\n| {{sort|108|1 season, 6 episodes}}\n| {{sort|021|21\u201328 min.}}\n| Ended<ref>{{cite tweet|last=Morrow|first=Michele|user=michelemorrow|number=977965053138812930|date=March 25, 2018|title=\u201c@YouTube cancelled Good Game\u201d #DisappointmentIn4Words|language=en|access-date=July 17, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''Long Distance''\n| Comedy\n| {{sort|2017-09-28|September 28, 2017}}\n| {{sort|101|1 season, 1 episode}}\n| {{sort|024|24 min.}}\n| Ended\n|-\n| ''[[Ryan Hansen Solves Crimes on Television]]''\n| Mystery/Comedy\n| {{sort|2017-10-25|October 25, 2017}}\n| {{sort|216|2 season, 16 episodes}}\n| {{sort|021|21\u201333 min.}}\n| Ended<ref name=\"Schneider\">{{Cite web|url=https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/ryan-hansen-solves-crimes-on-television-champaign-ill-canceled-youtube-1203185818/|title=\u2018Ryan Hansen,\u2019 \u2018Champaign ILL\u2019 Canceled as YouTube Prepares for New Originals Strategy (EXCLUSIVE)|last=Schneider|first=Michael|last2=Schneider|first2=Michael|date=2019-04-10|website=Variety|language=en|access-date=2019-04-10}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Do You Want To See a Dead Body?]]''\n| [[Surreal humor|Surreal comedy]]\n| {{sort|2017-11-17|November 17, 2017}}\n| {{sort|108|1 season, 15 episodes}}\n| {{sort|012|12\u201323 min.}}\n| Ended<ref name=\"Schneider\"/>\n|-\n| ''[[I'm Poppy]]''\n| Surreal comedy\n| {{sort|2018-01-25|January 25, 2018}}\n| {{sort|101|1 season, 1 episode}}\n| {{sort|012|23 min.}}\n| Pending\n|-\n| ''[[Youth & Consequences]]''\n| [[Teen drama|Teen]] [[Comedy-drama|dramedy]]\n| {{sort|2018-03-07|March 7, 2018}}\n| {{sort|101|1 season, 8 episodes}}\n| {{sort|026|26\u201334 min.}}\n| Ended<ref>{{cite tweet|last=Akana|first=Anna|user=AnnaAkana|number=1013132095240179723|date=June 30, 2018|title=Unfortunately we didn\u